    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "That's probably since they're on the same attribute, which isn't something we officially support I think. If the widgets are mounted in the other order, the result would be correct. I don't think we can really find a solution for that, except if toggle refinement doesn't remove other refinements in `getWidgetSearchParameters`",
